snippet.title: The Sims 4 Adventure Awaits | Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
The Sims™ 4 Adventure Awaits Expansion Pack* arrives Oct 2 and is available for pre-order now: https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/buy/addon/the-sims-4-adventure-awaits-expansion-pack

Order now through Nov 13 for the Warm & Cozy Digital Content**; the Toasty Tower Lamp, Toast-Tea Kettle, and Toasty Tootsies Socks.

Get inspiration for your next adventure: https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/news/adventure-awaits-expansion-pack

New experiences are out there for you to discover – or create! Make Getaways that last a day or more like a kids’ camp, fitness retreat, or even a romantic contest. Plus, create Custom Venues for Sims to explore and share them to the Gallery for other Simmers to enjoy.

Nurture the spirit of play in childhood and carry it through a bold, adventurous life. Kids will find their playtime more meaningful than ever with Childhood Sentiments, Imaginary Friends, and more ways to play like new games, Skills, and Modular Playgrounds you can customize.

Available October 2 at 10AM PT on EA App PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation®4, and PlayStation®5. Pre-order now: https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/buy/addon/the-sims-4-adventure-awaits-expansion-pack

*Requires The Sims 4 & all game updates. For PC, see minimum system requirements for the pack. **CONDITIONS AND RESTRICTIONS APPLY.

https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/buy/addon/the-sims-4-adventure-awaits-expansion-pack
